3. cs.PL (Programming Languages) is another possible category as the paper deals with the semantics of programs. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the construction of models. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with the semantics of programs, which is relevant to software engineering.
